      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of the S54-powered icon, preserved in concours condition. The 3.2L high-revving inline-six features individual throttle bodies and maintains factory-spec compression, with a recently serviced VANOS system ensuring precise variable valve timing. Power is routed through a tactile Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to a factory limited-slip differential. The chassis has undergone proactive subframe reinforcement and retains its original kinematic integrity with fresh OEM bushings. The exterior displays consistent paint depth across all panels, while the interior remains free of typical bolster wear or pixel degradation. This is a mechanically synchronized, turn-key investment for the discerning collector.",
